{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"0ad5e4e8a6","title":"关于在西沙群岛建立海军据点问题的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"1f22ac55d4","index":0,"year":1960,"month":8,"day":3,"articleId":"0ad5e4e8a6"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji43","name":"毛泽东全集第43卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/43-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji43":{"comments":[{"id":"db32a72aa4","publicationId":"maoquanji43","articleId":"0ad5e4e8a6","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这是毛泽东在中共中央军委1960年7月报告上写给中共中央军委秘书长、中国人民解放军总参谋长、国务院副总理罗瑞卿的批语。"},{"id":"9295d794ac","publicationId":"maoquanji43","articleId":"0ad5e4e8a6","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"中共中央军委的报告说：关于在西沙群岛建立海军据点问题，1959年3月，中央和周恩来同志已有批示，即海军在北确和宣德群岛定期巡逻成功后，可在永兴岛上建立海军据点。海军自1959年3月17日执行巡逻西沙任务以来，追今已历时一年又四个多月，共巡逻20次。为加强海南岛和西沙群岛的防务，加速西沙地区的经济开发，我们认为目前在永兴岛进行海军据点的建设，是必要的和适当的。在建设步骤上拟分两步进行：第一步建设营房、仓库、码头、雷达站等工程；第二步，在有利时机视情况再正式成立海军巡防区。"}],"contents":[{"id":"16667eb51e","type":"title","text":"关于在西沙群岛建立海军据点问题的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji43","articleId":"0ad5e4e8a6"},{"id":"db32a72aa4","type":"paragraph","text":"退罗瑞卿同志照办。回","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji43","articleId":"0ad5e4e8a6"},{"id":"9295d794ac","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji43","articleId":"0ad5e4e8a6"},{"id":"798e0e4d03","type":"paragraph","text":"八月三日","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji43","articleId":"0ad5e4e8a6"}],"page":{"id":"d09cc73e7b","publicationId":"maoquanji43","articleId":"0ad5e4e8a6","start":461,"end":461}}}},"__N_SSG":true}